00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:33,400
if we were mainly interested in motion along one axis

183
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:35,400
let's focus on that

184
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:37,400
motion along the x-axis

185
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:40,400
let's suppose there is no motion along y and z

186
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:43,400
then we can forget y and z for the moment

187
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,400
momentarily

