00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:45,400
I think the mathematicians are thinking of it independently

210
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:47,400
yeah, yeah, that's the point

211
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:48,400
that is the point, yes

212
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:51,400
they're thinking of time as the independent variable

213
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:53,400
and everybody knows

214
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:57,400
that it's a law of nature that the independent variable should be horizontal

