00:13:08,400 --> 00:13:12,400
let's take his origin of spatial coordinates

219
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:16,400
his origin of spatial coordinates at time t equals zero

220
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:19,400
is just at the same, let's assume that

