00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:41,400
I'm the x prime coordinate over there, right?

229
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:43,400
I'm the x prime coordinates

230
00:13:43,400 --> 00:13:45,400
and of course I being very egocentric

231
00:13:45,400 --> 00:13:50,400
