00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:20,400
that's a straight line

245
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:23,400
and it's moving with velocity v

246
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:26,400
which means it's x prime equals

247
00:14:26,400 --> 00:14:30,400
sorry, it means x equals vt

